\f4\b0 \cf0 \strokec3 \{\cf6 \strokec6 \\bfseries\cf0 \strokec3  Semantic compatibility principle:\}\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \strokec6 \\quad\cf0 \strokec3  Semantic compatibility is a precursor to semantic interoperability. both agents must make their ontological commitment underlying their domain models, explicit.\cf5 \strokec5 \\end\cf0 \strokec3 \{\ul mmdp\ulnone \} \
